scripts.build-react: yarn run clean-react && node scripts/generate-react.js && cpr README.md publish-react/README.md -o && cpr CHANGELOG.md publish-react/CHANGELOG.md -o && cpr LICENSE publish-react/LICENSE -o
scripts.build-solid: node scripts/generate-solid.js && cpr README.md publish-solid/README.md -o && cpr CHANGELOG.md publish-solid/CHANGELOG.md -o && cpr LICENSE publish-solid/LICENSE -o
scripts.build-preact: yarn run clean-preact && yarn run generate-preact-readme && node scripts/generate-preact.js && cpr README-preact.md publish-preact/README.md -o && cpr CHANGELOG.md publish-preact/CHANGELOG.md -o && cpr LICENSE publish-preact/LICENSE -o
